version_description:
- Matches are now shown in the rightmost page. Before, it would only show people who asked you out that you matched with, now it shows people you asked out and people who asked out you.
- Login with Instagram, Facebook, or Twitter -- incase you forgot your password
- Now you can change your city from the Settings page
- Now you can change what genders you see from the Settings page
- Made it clearer when you've already asked someone out, and if you match, it'll show their contact info
